{"tid":1640300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］又更正喎 係刑期上訴喎","createTime":"2019-10-09T02:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T02:42:56.000Z","uid":37626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"da695e4ce403a175e9df9a6d3f7622ecdc17ee53","tid":1640300,"uid":37626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMzidbD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMzidbD.png&h=f3cdf9c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83ddb05445657b4cbcb05ba3435d183866743ea8","tid":1640300,"uid":37626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36674fcc2b96eff008843bdcdcb68885ddc97d5e","tid":1640300,"uid":37626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856f2720d67206fd93578a8b285b90c04085f1c7","tid":1640300,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:06:59.000Z","msg":"（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"3d1c37f880ffdb3b3245672c413b520fa2ab7a16","tid":1640300,"uid":37626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4284548e68c9ebd85f275843e8a4b1602f8f65ab","tid":1640300,"uid":37626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338da0996d080f9381e5dffaa151511847fff417","tid":1640300,"uid":37626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b47a3069f9f456a2bff4e1fb4bac6ba0c6a1d7","tid":1640300,"uid":37626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1956edbf035203f8389723e9b93549176856fe9a","tid":1640300,"uid":76364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:08:46.000Z","msg":"好混亂...<br />\n會唔會等陣又改<br />\n但無論點我都希望佢成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6970e4f5ebe75894e76dcaa4abed33858a003657","tid":1640300,"uid":152938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"瘋狂炒車"},{"pid":"e84ed63fd47e1ba8982b85d3f33a65335b97a102","tid":1640300,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18103cb27f63494c14e1ca4cc0332a7f117674e7","tid":1640300,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019